          <p>In Europe, buildings are designed to last 100+ years. In America, the focus has shifted toward faster construction and lower initial costs. But what happens when hurricanes, extreme heat, and time test these structures?</p>
          <p>We respect both traditions, but we believe Texas deserves the best of both worlds: European durability adapted for American living.</p>
